878
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,550
Siguro gawa-gawa lang ng accountant

879
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,750
at ginawan ng mali ang kaniyang asawa.

880
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:19,710
