-Nasaan ang ate mo?

928
00:36:31,400 --> 00:36:33,300
Pumunta si Zhao sa tindahan.

929
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,160
Takot na takot ako.

930
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,280
