953
00:38:15,600 --> 00:38:16,730
Nasaan si Zhang Ling?

954
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:18,270
Bakit wala siya rito para makita ako?

955
00:38:18,270 --> 00:38:18,970
Panginoon ko.

956
00:38:19,110 --> 00:38:20,990
Nakipagsabwatan si Lord Zhang
sa mangangalakal ng butil na si Song Wenhe

957
00:38:20,990 --> 00:38:21,840
