958
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:22,740
Isa itong karumal-dumal na krimen.

959
00:38:22,740 --> 00:38:23,770
Hinubaran siya ng Kanyang Kamahalan

960
00:38:23,770 --> 00:38:25,700
