961
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:27,440
Nasangkot din ba siya?

962
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,760
Pagkatapos ang Kumander ng Hukumang Penal

963
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:30,400
